<br>
Here's how I rate the special flavors from the best (as in I can actually swallow the bean) to worst (one bite and I'll never let one near my lips again):<br>
<br>
Dirt (really tastes like dirt... too weird)<br>
Grass<br>
Spinach<br>
Black Pepper<br>
Booger<br>
Sardine<br>
Ear Wax<br>
Vomit<br>
<br>
I'm curious... do any of you parents actually have kids that EAT them? hehe, I can't imagine actually chomping them down after my brush with some of the yuckier flavors, but as a kid, who knows?<br>
